9:50 AM Defendant Dilvinder G Singh in court, in custody.  Attorney Nicole Marie Ostrowski in court for Dilvinder G Singh.  Plaintiff State of Wisconsin in court.  Attorney Lindsey Hirt in court for State of Wisconsin.

State requests a doctor to be appointed from the Behavioral Consultants.  Court suggests two doctors be appointed through the Behavioral Consultants and Dr. Tyre is appointed as an evaluating doctor.
